{"tid":517240,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"用保力加線計買入時機其實有冇效?","createTime":"2018-01-02T06:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T09:32:58.000Z","uid":70429,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"fca79ca7bc19ef2caf3a5a066391944dae4fd805","tid":517240,"uid":70429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T06:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/loqhjvbc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Floqhjvbc&h=52ceb4db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上禮拜5我睇恆指係通道頂(果陣仲穿埋),屬於賣出訊號,咁我就就買左小注500蚊30600打靶熊諗住測試下保力加理論究竟有冇效.<br />\n<br />\n今早起身一睇,<br />\n<br />\n開市已經3萬,<br />\n<br />\n開市10分鐘升360點,<br />\n<br />\n10點升450點.<br />\n<br />\n12點上半場打完講緊500點升幅.<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> .<br />\n<br />\n500蚊熊變150蚊.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據個垃圾理論,佢掂到通道頂屬於賣出訊號,會開始回落<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以1月3號會回落嗎?我覺得好似3萬1勢如破竹了.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學藝未精,屌細力d.<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00fb716a65a72a1be337bcdf86aea14fb73a561c","tid":517240,"uid":63934,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T06:47:15.000Z","msg":"從來買股都唔會淨睇一兩個指標決定"},{"pid":"5b6db02d7972afbb63141ec391a564fa1b275bd5","tid":517240,"uid":38172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T07:19:05.000Z","msg":"從來都唔會咁玩牛熊, 你咁樣估頂估底, 多多唔夠你輸"},{"pid":"8c2055064bfe551bd5afc836b519f2e017e843df","tid":517240,"uid":28410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T07:24:16.000Z","msg":"睇開就知係馬後炮指標<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60af01a47949f74cf6bf65aca01394e85ad14b24","tid":517240,"uid":4691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T07:37:35.000Z","msg":"破頂當日會見到陽燭隊穿通道頂，之後條通道會闊左。<br />\n強勢股連破52週高，會貼住通道頂上。如果每破一次頂入一次熊，多多都唔夠輸。"},